snippet.textDisplay:
I got the CORSAIR Virtuoso RGB Wireless for some time now...
Let me tell you:
It's really heavy, the Headband is not comfortable, neither are the cushions for ppl with glasses, and music doesn't sound great even after cranking the EQ. Oh and the Wireless Range istn't great either (maybe 8 meters). Software can be buggy too, obviously (what did you expect from corsair right?).
But USB-C is nice and battery lasts long enough and you can also use it plugged in.
Feel free to ask me.
